com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core

Class ValueNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core.Node
      • com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core.ValueNode<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Session, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<ValueNode<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayValue, Record, SingleValue

    public abstract class ValueNode<T>
extends Node
implements Comparable<ValueNode<T>>, Cloneable
    ValueNode is the base class for all persistent values held in fields and arrays. Values can be:
    • Single values (boolean, date, string, etc. -- see FieldType)
    • Records
    • Array of single values, records, and arrays
      See Also:
      SingleValue, Record, ArrayValue, Node, Field, FieldType, Serialized Form
